OL,6,FBusiness owner Joanna Corder said: "I
OL,7,Ffind it very hard to believe that we
OL,8,Fare getting a good deal at the moment
OL,9,Fbecause of the way that I feel that we
OL,10,Fare sometimes treated by individuals
OL,11,Fin Guernsey, not by the island as a
OL,12,Fwhole.
OL,14,F"I appreciate the review because I
OL,15,Fhope it's going to show that everyone
OL,16,Fis doing their best (to get a fair
OL,17,Fdeal)."
