OL,3,CAlderney's top politician says review
OL,4,Cinto economic deal is 'sensible'
OL,6,FGuernsey's Chief Minister, Deputy
OL,7,FLyndon Trott, said: "Strong and
OL,8,Fresilient transport links are critical
OL,9,Fto the success of island communities.
OL,10,FHowever, we cannot ignore the
OL,11,Fchallenging fiscal situation that the
OL,12,FStates of Guernsey finds itself in.
OL,14,FHe added: "The time has come for a
OL,15,Fradical reconsideration of this
OL,16,Fproject. It is necessary to find a
OL,17,Ffunctional solution, that can achieve
OL,18,Fa reasonable level of connectivity for
OL,19,Fthe Alderney community within the
OL,20,Fcurrent financial limits of the States
OL,21,Fof Guernsey.
