OL,3,CAlderney's top politician says review
OL,4,Cinto economic deal is 'sensible'
OL,6,F"It is clear to the Policy & Resources
OL,7,FCommittee that there is a serious need
OL,8,Ffor a constitutional committee,
OL,9,Festablished collaboratively with the
OL,10,Fother islands, that can focus on
OL,11,Freviewing the relationships within the
OL,12,FBailiwick and make recommendations for
OL,13,Fthe parliaments of the islands to
OL,14,Fconsider."
OL,16,FThe review will also look at relations
OL,17,Fbetween Guernsey and Sark.
